ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:33:31.000Z","msg":"將來我應該都係咁, 只係隔離可能多一個1:1矽膠娃娃"},{"pid":"77f5da00f05ab21dd216680bd727c4b54126ce20","tid":547131,"uid":17753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:34:47.000Z","msg":"人類個陣屍臭味聞過一次真係永世難忘<br />\n尤其腐爛咗生哂屍蟲個啲就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好佩服"},{"pid":"1ff8969f4093d3277b9a43ffe8d35a4665492422","tid":547131,"uid":20072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13cb315050ceadc5b7edc8dece71eb78233a0562","tid":547131,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9616f1c6ca1bc5ddf76d33e53f6be4d502f2729","tid":547131,"uid":53026,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T07:35:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>弘明曾經離婚，在日產汽車、富士通等大企業任職系統工程師逾20年，但一直都只是低薪沒有福利的合約工</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nIT合約工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"日本it狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大公司都係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:41:11.000Z","msg":"做廿年都係咁, 唔轉工"}]}